        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0100</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>SpeechToType 1.1</h2>
                <p>Major feature update with new capabilities!</p>
                <h3>New Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Recording Overlay</strong>: Visual indicator with sound wave animation while recording</li>
                    <li><strong>Continuous Recording</strong>: Double-tap the hotkey to record without holding</li>
                    <li><strong>Text Rewriting</strong>: Select text and use AI to correct grammar, elaborate, or apply custom prompts</li>
                    <li><strong>Customizable Shortcuts</strong>: Configure your own keyboard shortcuts for all functions</li>
                    <li><strong>GPT Model Selection</strong>: Choose between GPT-4o, GPT-5, and GPT-5.2 for text rewriting</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed API key input in onboarding</li>
                    <li>Improved settings organization</li>
                    <li>Enhanced localization for German and English</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
